{"tid":2138726,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple 的 Secure Enclave 晶片被揭「不可修補」的漏洞","createTime":"2020-08-03T19:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T09:17:27.000Z","uid":62253,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7d48b8eadb8777bae88b635e245126119bbe9d15","tid":2138726,"uid":62253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T19:30:48.000Z","msg":"大家睇路，小心黃之鋒事件再發生<br />\n<br />\n英文原文: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://9to5mac.com/2020/08/01/new-unpatchable-exploit-allegedly-found-on-apples-secure-enclave-chip-heres-what-it-could-mean/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F9to5mac.com%2F2020%2F08%2F01%2Fnew-unpatchable-exploit-allegedly-found-on-apples-secure-enclave-chip-heres-what-it-could-mean%2F&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O6WONrq76Y1XZ%2F%2BBeLOBzgc%3D&h=89bdc091\" target=\"_blank\">https://9to5mac.com/2020/08/01/new-unpatchable-exploit-allegedly-found-on-apples-secure-enclave-chip-heres-what-it-could-mean/</a><br />\n<br />\n據 9to5mac 報導， 在 Mosec 2020 大會上，中國越獄團隊 Pangu (盤古) 發現了 Secure Enclave 安全協處理器上的一個「不可修補」的漏洞。這可能會讓 iPhone、iPad、Mac、Apple Watch 和其他 Apple 設備處於危險當中。<br />\n<br />\nApple 的 Secure Enclave 晶片可以加密和保護設備上儲存的所有敏感數據 ，是為設備帶來安全的保障晶片。Secure Enclave 安全協處理器幾乎是 Apple 產品的標準配置，它能為設備提供額外的安全保護，使用隨機密鑰對數據進行加密，只有 Secure Enclave 才能讀取。<br />\n這些密鑰對使用者的設備來說是獨一無二的，而且也絕不會與 iCloud 同步。除了加密使用者的檔案之外，Secure Enclave 還負責存儲管理敏感數據的密鑰，如密碼、Apple Pay 使用的信用卡，甚至是你的生物特徵識別以啟用 Touch ID 和 Face ID。這令到黑客更難在沒有密碼的情況下獲取你的個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n而今次越獄團隊盤古所說的漏洞「不可修補」意味著該漏洞存在於硬件而不是軟件中，因此已出廠的設備可能無法修復這一問題。<br />\n目前配搭有 Secure Enclave 晶片的設備包括：<br />\niPhone 5s及更高版本<br />\n<br />\niPad（第5代）及更高版本<br />\n<br />\niPad Air（第一代）及更高版本<br />\n<br />\niPad mini 2及更高版本<br />\n<br />\niPad Pro<br />\n<br />\n帶有 T1 或 T2 晶片的設備：<br />\nApple TV HD（第4代）及更高版本<br />\n<br />\nApple Watch Series 1 及更高版本<br />\n<br />\nHomePod<br />\n<br />\n目前，盤古團隊並沒有進一步說明該漏洞的細節，但如果能夠完全讀取 Security Enclave 數據，這意味著黑客就有機會可以獲得使用者的密碼、信用卡等信息。目前我們唯一知道的是，Secure Enclave 的這個漏洞會影響到 A7 和 A11 Bionic 之間的所有 Apple 產品，涉及範圍十分之廣。而 Apple 方面暫時仍未有任何回應，所以實際影響有多少暫時還不清楚。<br />\n<br />\nSource :<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.style.yahoo.com/apple-%E7%9A%84-secure-enclave-%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%AD-093359281.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.style.yahoo.com%2Fapple-%25E7%259A%2584-secure-enclave-%25E6%2599%25B6%25E7%2589%2587%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258F%25AD-093359281.html&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O6WONrq76Y1XZ%2F%2BBeLOBzgc%3D&h=a4fc59a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.style.yahoo.com/apple-%E7%9A%84-secure-enclave-%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%AD-093359281.html</a>"},{"pid":"a91c3b2769d77c18e4bc7d11e98a867d17a88c6e","tid":2138726,"uid":158977,"like":12,"dislike":13,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T19:42:49.000Z","msg":"啱啱好 可以出部pixel 4a<br />\n周庭win"},{"pid":"6db3c9533c277ecca236ef37a6b0eb226e97cfc3","tid":2138726,"uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T19:45:35.000Z","msg":"好彩係a12"},{"pid":"5a6ba409799aaed5b16b791465ccc6726faac285","tid":2138726,"uid":62253,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"6db3c9533c277ecca236ef37a6b0eb226e97cfc3","tid":2138726,"uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T19:45:35.000Z","msg":"好彩係a12"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T19:47:24.000Z","msg":"你呢個係講緊checkm8 漏洞 (即iPhone X 或之前機種)，但而家係講緊一個全新嘅漏洞"},{"pid":"9f5bb256ae2ca22fbf4380bb98b9157ac135b2ca","tid":2138726,"uid":6848,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"5a6ba409799aaed5b16b791465ccc6726faac285","tid":2138726,"uid":62253,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"6db3c9533c277ecca236ef37a6b0eb226e97cfc3","tid":2138726,"uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T19:45:35.000Z","msg":"好彩係a12"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T19:47:24.000Z","msg":"你呢個係講緊checkm8 漏洞 (即iPhone X 或之前機種)，但而家係講緊一個全新嘅漏洞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T20:00:33.000Z","msg":"目前我們唯一知道的是，Secure Enclave 的這個漏洞會影響到 A7 和 A11 Bioni